Package: CERFIT
Version: 0.1.0
Title: Causal Effect Random Forest of Interaction Tress
Author: Justin Thorp  [aut, cre], Luo Li [aut], Juanjuan Fan [aut]
Maintainer: Justin Thorp <jjtthorp@gmail.com>
Description: Fits a Causal Effect Random Forest of Interaction Tress (CERFIT) which is a modification of the Random Forest algorithm where each split is chosen to maximize subgroup treatment heterogeneity. Doing this allows it to estimate the individualized treatment effect for each observation in either RCT or observational data.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
